ww.crimsontwilight.org/upload/xylor/swirl.jpg WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   prices and the drinal market in general</span><hr size=1> Well wasnt sure if to just add to:<br>
