For people in lesser guilds or that freelance, these mobs are going to be out of there reach for many months to come.  Once you hit 60, platinum becomes worthless other then for horses, peridots, coffins, pearls, food, drink and twinking.  There is no armor at 60 that you can buy to upgrade yourself, its all mostly no drop or quested.  So why not spend all your plat on a spell you otherwise wouldnt see for many months?<br>
